-- China Stock Trading Account Openings Increase 162% in Week Ended June 25
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-29T23:58:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/china-stock-trading-account-openings-increase-162-in-week-ended-june-25.html

          
          
             Investors opened 162 percent more
accounts for trading Chinese stocks during the week ended June
25 as compared with a week earlier, according to the China
Securities Depository and Clearing Corp.  
 Investors opened 292,805 accounts during the week,
according to the clearing house.  
